<p id="fs-idp251836720">(e) Cl, Cs, Ge, H, Sr</p>
</div>
</div>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-idp31566784">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idp186425376">
<p id="fs-idp65374912">Which atoms can bond to sulfur so as to produce a positive partial charge on the sulfur atom?</p>
</div>
<div data-type="solution" id="fs-idp77775472">
<p id="fs-idm121823728">N, O, F, and Cl</p>
</div>
</div>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-idp9464672">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idp10397696">
